This paper proposes a neural network-based model for a recommendation system that integrates rating scores prediction and explainable words generation. This involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques, which suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, and cs.CY. The paper discusses the use of collaborative filtering algorithms, which is a common technique in recommender systems, and this could also suggest that the paper belongs to the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
